 1995-14261995-08-290AGRI-FOOD,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisAmendment to Orders in Council P.C. 1986-1761 of July 23, 1986, P.C. 1987-1109 of June 1, 1987 and P.C. 1988-1322 of June 28, 1988 terminating the two Farm Debt Review Boards in Alberta, Saskatchewan, Manitoba and Ontario; establishment of a single provincial Farm Debt Review Board in each of these provinces; and appointment of certain persons as Chairmen of the provincial Farm Debt Review Boards. (JAMES WAARDENBURG, Matsqui, British Columbia; DENNIS MERLIN HUEPPELSHEUSER, Blackfalds, Alberta; EARL KEELER, Delisle, Saskatchewan; GARNET MILTON KYLE, Dominion City, Manitoba; GEORGE McLAUGHLIN, Beaverton, Ontario; JEAN-PAUL CLOUTIER, Ste-Foy, Quebec; DAVID VINCENT DAVIES, Port Williams, Nova Scotia; ROBERT IRVING MacKENZIE, Hartsville, Prince Edward Island; and HECTOR WILLIAMS, Goulds, Newfoundland)
